49f2eb46-75c3-47e9-90aa-80586aa09174.title: Chaeldar
49f2eb46-75c3-47e9-90aa-80586aa09174.text: 'Ello, and what are you after then?

options.text: Have you any rewards for me, or anything to trade?
Let's talk about the difficulty of my assignments.

e1cb1476-4144-4ee3-8a45-e033c9fe5d5a.title: Chaeldar
e1cb1476-4144-4ee3-8a45-e033c9fe5d5a.text:
You are too low of a combat level, come back when,
you are more experienced.

d8d05b77-3647-4c17-9541-421c3ca175ab.title: Chaeldar
d8d05b77-3647-4c17-9541-421c3ca175ab.text:
You're still meant to be slaying <slayer_task_type>(s),
you have <slayer_task_remaining> to go.

85ec4547-ae91-410d-a0cd-41a53d3c724d.title: <player>
85ec4547-ae91-410d-a0cd-41a53d3c724d.text: Have you any rewards for me, or anything to trade?

ebfa9c0a-636e-4a45-8d0f-0005d09a407b.title: Chaeldar
ebfa9c0a-636e-4a45-8d0f-0005d09a407b.text:
I have quite a few rewards you can earn, and a wide
variety of Slayer equipment for sale.

85ada798-51e3-4ae3-9f75-32ff1e12880c.title: <player>
85ada798-51e3-4ae3-9f75-32ff1e12880c.text: Let's talk about the difficulty of my assignments.

8a5d71df-6bf5-4b3c-b057-b3fe619682d4.title: Chaeldar
8a5d71df-6bf5-4b3c-b057-b3fe619682d4.text:
The Slayer Masters will take your combat level into
account when choosing tasks for you, so you shouldn't
get anything too hard.

6d28e505-7027-435f-b6dd-900e968f567c.title: <player>
6d28e505-7027-435f-b6dd-900e968f567c.text: That's fine - I don't want anything too tough.
